# UI & Styling Standards

- **Typography**: Use `font-satoshi` for body/labels and `font-roundo` for headings.
- **Roundo Font Rule**: All text using `font-roundo` must be lowercase - always.
- **Glassmorphism Formula**: 
  - Background: `bg-white/10` or `bg-black/20`
  - Blur: `backdrop-blur-md`
  - Border: `border border-white/20`
- **Naming Convention**: 
  - `Comp_`: Reusable atoms (Buttons, Badges)
  - `Layout_`: Page-level containers
  - `Chat_`: Chat-specific elements
- **Precision**: If design uses 13px, use Tailwind arbitrary values `p-[13px]`.
